content.title: On Earth
content.content:
1918 - J.R.R. Tolkien attends a medical board examination. He is based with 9th Royal Defence Corps at Easington.
1965 - J.R.R. Tolkien writes Letter 268.
1996 - The Tolkien Ensemble have their first concert at Gjorslev Castle, Denmark.
